# LiveKit Plugins DeepGram

Agent Framework plugin for speech-to-text with [DeepGram](mdc:https:/deepgram.com)'s API. Currently supports speech-to-text.

## Installation

```bash
pip install livekit-plugins-deepgram
```

## Pre-requisites

Requires an API key from DeepGram. It can be set as an environment variable: `DEEPGRAM_API_KEY`
